"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Isolating and positioning the vas during vasectomy",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 360px; height: 337px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The vas deferens is positioned to lie as superficially as possible. A \"three finger technique\" is used to manipulate the vas within the scrotum using the non-dominant hand.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Reproduced with permission from: Clenney, TL, Higgins, JC. Vasectomy Techniques. American Family Physician 1999; 60:137. Copyright &copy;1999 Timothy Clenney, MD, MPH.",
